The paper deals with the effects of interference on mobile communication systems in the presence of fading, shadowing, and noise. This topic is closely related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), networked systems (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), and mobile computing (cs.MA). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
